*,
*::after,
*::before {
  /*box-sizing: border-box;*/ /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height: */
  box-sizing: inherit; /* herda body */
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}



::before
- Insere algo antes do elemento.
p::before{ content: "Read this: " }



::after
- Insere algo depois do elemento.
p::after{ content: "Remember this: " }



::selection
- Edita o texto que o usu√°rio seleciona.
- color, background, cursor, and outline.



